Megger and IPS Group announce strategic partnership
Megger Group ('Megger') and IPS Group ('IPS') jointly announce that they have reached a definitive agreement to work together as strategic partners combining both their experience and product lines to create new value for the electrical supply industry. The agreement includes Megger taking an equity stake in IPS.
